# Cloudflare Pages headers (https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/headers/).
# Intentionally conservative: the bundles load React/Babel from a CDN and use
# inline scripts/styles, so no Content-Security-Policy is set here (it would
# break them). These two are safe and apply to every response.
/*
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
